# Drop the launcher / splash assets here:
#   app_icon.png             (1024×1024, opaque)
#   app_icon_foreground.png  (foreground layer, adaptive icon)
#   splash.png               (used by flutter_native_splash)
#   splash_android12.png     (Android 12 splash, 1152×1152 centred)
#
# After replacing these PNGs, run:
#   make icons
#   make splash
